♪ Brakeman, blow your whistle ♪

53:19.566 --> 53:23.066
♪ Throw your weight Upon the chain ♪

53:23.133 --> 53:27.500
♪ Make way Whatever will be, will be ♪

53:29.466 --> 53:34.300
♪ Between the Sandman The Brakeman, and me ♪

